{"tid":445282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍贏大選 日圓兌港元見6.86！","createTime":"2017-10-23T08:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T09:05:28.000Z","uid":20058,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bb9ebfeb326493bd9b2668742e32708909ae67","tid":445282,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"日本首相安倍晉三執政聯盟，在眾議院選舉取得超過三份之二的議席。市場預料「安倍經濟學」將會持續，預計安倍政府將繼續執行寬鬆的貨幣政策。<br />\n<br />\n日圓受壓，兌美元一度升穿114，今早見114.09，為3個月低位，於中午12時54分報113.73。兌港元方面，每百日圓兌港元跌125點子，最新報6.8605，是遊日人士兌錢的好時機！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171023&amp;guid=57366336&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171023%26guid%3D57366336%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=qcVwwde9oMbtbm8DsRA4GU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=268d451b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171023%26guid%3D57366336%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=bdd41e91\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171023&amp;guid=57366336&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"7f980b60eefd7a1ef9167af84b4e439ae30d835d","tid":445282,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"去百年排隊先"}]}